    "created_at": "2015-01-26T18:19:03Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-01-26T18:19:03Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "From the dev meeting last week: we'd prefer this to be a context manager, perhaps even in matplotlib (see e.g. [switch_backend()](http://matplotlib.org/api/pyplot_api.html#matplotlib.pyplot.switch_backend)), but enabling and disabling the inline backend may require hooks after the cell's execution, in which case it couldn't be implemented as a context manager, and we'd consider this approach.\n\nHowever, at this point, we'd like to leave it until after IPython 3.0, which we are trying to get ready for release. Setting the milestone to 4.0.\n"
  },
